<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #666;
    }
    .token-link {
      word-break: break-all;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
    <p>You recently requested to reset your password for your TravelTales account.</p>
    <p>Click the button below to reset it. This link will expire in <strong>15 minutes</strong> for your security.</p>

    <p>
      <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
    </p>

    <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste the link below into your browser:</p>
    <p class="token-link"><%= resetLink %></p>

    <p>If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>– The TravelTales Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
